      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>>@Compendium[sfrpg.class-features.D1aTODGCokdl7pZl]{Shadow}</p>\n<p>As a move action, you can spend 1 Resolve Point to shroud yourself in dim light for 1 minute. Darkvision provides no benefit against this gloom, and nonmagical light can&rsquo;t change this light level. Magical light can change this light level only if from a source with a CR or level higher than yours. You can dismiss this dim light as a move action, and it ends automatically if you lose consciousness.</p>"
